 The Vortex GSM Server -Introduction-

 What is GSM ?

 GSM is a form of speech compression used world wide with mobile phones and
 other such devices. Play back is ay 8khz (the same as real audio)

 What does that have to do with me ?

 Theres a program on Aminet (GIR06.lha) which allows you to listen to
 files encoded using gsm until recently threre were very few sites which
 actually had anything worth listening to , but now thats changed.....

 How has it changed ?

 Two months ago the Vortex gsm server was created with the help of a few
 tools created by the author of GIR06 and by Fortunecity being a very
 generous free web space provider (not to mention tripod also being good).
 The server was intially set up for use by the members of @{"vORTEX" link "vortexinfo" 0} but now
 the site is ready to be used by everyone.
 (note: because the site is hosted by fortunecity slow connects and general
 unsmoothness of play back should be expected , find out how to help with
 that @{"HERE" link "support" 0})

 And thats How the vORTEX gSM sERVER was created.
