                     What When Why and Where

 What can I find at on Server ?

 At the Vortex server you will find song that are in gsm format for you to
 listen over the internet in realtime or that you can download and listen
 to them (the best option if you have a 14.4 or less? modem)
 The server web site is also where you can download GIR06 full version from
 aminet or a smaller quick start version, the most uptodate version of the
 prefs file is also available from the site aswell.



 When is it Updated ?

 As a rule it is updated once a fortnight , but if there is a song that i
 particularly like i will most likely sample it and upload it sooner, there
 is a mailing list you can join to keep uptodate with when the site is
 updated & changed.

 Why do you do it ?

 Good Question.

 Where is the 'vORTEX gSM Sever' ?

 At the moment the server is located with FortuneCity and Tripod
 (both free web site providers) but as Im hoping this will change to
 a more reliable and less busy server so that the gsm streams flow smooth
 90% of the time the site can be located at http://vtx.home.ml.org
 (free domain courtest of www.ml.org) if you bookmark the above url
 you will always be at the most recent version of the server.
